'''Ian Gibson''' ([[1940s#1946|1946]]<ref name="born" /> &ndash; [[December 11]], [[2023]]<ref name="dead" />) was a [[Star Wars comic books|comic book]] illustrator who worked on ''[[Star Wars: Boba Fett: Enemy of the Empire]] and [[Star Wars: Droids: Rebellion]]''. Outside of his Star Wars work, he was known for his contributions to [[Wikipedia:2000 AD (comics)|''2000 AD'']], including [[Wikipedia:Judge Dredd|''Judge Dredd'']], [[Wikipedia:The Ballad of Halo Jones|''The Ballad of Halo Jones'']] and [[Wikipedia:Robo Hunter|''Robo Hunter'']].<ref name="born" />

